    <item>
      <title>Lo specchio impossibile.</title>
      <link>http://uriel-fanelli.github.io/blogger/2014-04-09-lo-specchio-impossibile/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Apr 2014 12:15:50 +0100</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://uriel-fanelli.github.io/blogger/2014-04-09-lo-specchio-impossibile/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;h1&gt;{{ page.title }}&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;div class=&#39;post&#39;&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;Uno dei motivi per cui e&amp;rsquo; bello scrivere e&amp;rsquo; che (persino nelle vicissitudini che capitano quando i soliti ci si mettono) e&amp;rsquo; che si e&amp;rsquo; portati ad indagare le proprie ragioni.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;Voglio dire, innanzitutto l&amp;rsquo;idea di chiudere il blog e&amp;rsquo; un&amp;rsquo;idea che mi ha dato un senso di soffocamento, e contemporaneamente ha contribuito a spiegare a me stesso&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222; font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;per quale ragione scrivo, nel mio caso &amp;ldquo;irrequietezza&amp;rdquo;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;a name=&#39;more&#39;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;Ma nello scrivere, anche su un diario (pubblico o meno) quel che si pensa, si finisce sempre per descrivere cio&amp;rsquo; che si e&amp;rsquo;, ed e&amp;rsquo; per questo che scrivere aiuta.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;Negli ultimi due giorni ho dovuto accettare persone per questo gruppo, e ho ricevuto diverse &amp;ldquo;presentazioni&amp;rdquo; (le avevo inventate perche&amp;rsquo; esiste un &amp;ldquo;writing fingerprint&amp;rdquo; che permette&amp;nbsp;di identificare il modo di pensare delle persone ) ma sto iniziando a notare una cosa. Ovvero, la incredibilmente bassa opinione che le persone hanno di se&amp;rsquo;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;Ora, torniamo indietro un attimo.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;Ammettiamo anche che da qui non usciranno premi nobel. Ok. Quindi non mi aspetto che qualcuno arrivi e dica &amp;ldquo;ciao, sono il futuro premio Nobel&amp;rdquo;. Benissimo.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;Tuttavia, partite dall&amp;rsquo;idea che volete essere iscritti perche&amp;rsquo; vi piace leggere quello che scrivo, che in qualche modo trovate che sia differente dal resto. Ok, siete anche disposti&amp;nbsp;a spendere tempo per la mia logorrea, cosa che significa che volete &amp;ldquo;investire&amp;rdquo; in qualcosa che secondo voi beneficia in qualche modo la vostra mente.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;Non discuto le vostre scelte, ma&amp;hellip; perche&amp;rsquo; tanto odio? Voglio dire, nel pensare di chiudere io ho capito che scrivo per una cosa che si chiama &amp;ldquo;irrequietezza&amp;rdquo;. Benissimo.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;Comunque voi chiamiate la forza che vi spinge a leggere, diciamo &amp;ldquo;esplorazione&amp;rdquo;. Allora, voi state &amp;ldquo;esplorando&amp;rdquo; e qualcosa ha attirato la vostra attenzione.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;Va bene. Ma in questo senso, siete gia&amp;rsquo; un gradino al di sopra della media delle persone, che ha smesso di esplorare, e di fatto si limita a portare a spasso un tubo digerente&amp;nbsp;e attende la morte avendo cura di produrre piu&amp;rsquo; rifiuti ed escrementi possibili. Ma supponiamo anche che NON siate migliori della media. Il fatto di voler leggere qualcosa&amp;nbsp;di certo non vi qualifica come mentecatti.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;Ma non e&amp;rsquo; questo che leggo tra le &amp;ldquo;presentazioni&amp;rdquo; e&amp;rsquo; un insieme di persone ad autostima bassissima. Non e&amp;rsquo; che io sia di quelli che devono camminare sulla carbonella&amp;nbsp;per avere successo o una specie di Visconte Cobram che vuole arrivare in Tibet con la bicicletta senza sella , ma &amp;hellip; diavolo, non vi rendete conto di essere vittime di una specie&amp;nbsp;di effetto Pigmalione al contrario, che vi ha convinti di essere delle merde?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;Nell&amp;rsquo;uso comune, dice la Treccani, un pigmalione e&amp;rsquo;&amp;nbsp; chi assume il ruolo di maestro nei confronti di persona rozza e incolta, spec. una donna, plasmandone la personalit√†,&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;sviluppandone le doti naturali e affinandone i modi.&amp;nbsp; Nella leggenda, Pigmalione crea una statua di avorio, della quale si innamora, e chiede ad Afrodite di farne una donna&amp;nbsp;da sposare, ovvero crea, in un certo senso, la donna che sta cercando partendo da materia piu&amp;rsquo; bruta.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;Un effetto Pigmalione al contrario, dunque, e&amp;rsquo; l&amp;rsquo;effetto per il quale qualcuno che non vuole essere superato in una gara qualsiasi convinca i propri concorrenti di non&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;essere in grado di sostenere la gara.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;Un professore mediocre a scuola, dei colleghi mediocri, un capo mediocre: tutti hanno l&amp;rsquo;interesse a demotivarvi, a convincervi di valere poco, di non essere capaci&amp;nbsp;di nulla. Non posso ovviamente prendere quel che scrivete come esempio, ma posso cercare di riassumere la descrizione che mediamente date di voi:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;blockquote class=&#34;tr_bq&#34; style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;i style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;Ciao Uriel, sono un peone senza intelligenza. Faccio un lavoro di merda, vivo in un posto di merda, e sono cosi&amp;rsquo; vuoto che ho bisogno di leggere quel che&amp;nbsp;scrivi per avere la sensazione di essere vivo. Non ho neanche il coraggio di cambiare e sono una persona grigia e vuota.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;Certo, non lo scrivete cosi&amp;rsquo;, ma di fatto il giro di parole non e&amp;rsquo; nemmeno mai troppo lontano da questo.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;Non e&amp;rsquo; che io voglia una specie di Pessimisti Anonimi o una setta, ma &amp;hellip; davvero? Davvero ognuno di voi pensa di essere questo, e davvero pensate&amp;nbsp;che la descrizione che date di voi sia reale?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;Qui c&amp;rsquo;e&amp;rsquo; un punto chiave: statisticamente, non puo&amp;rsquo; essere cosi&amp;rsquo;. Io non ho scritto da nessuna parte &amp;ldquo;se vi dichiarate delle merde allora e&amp;rsquo; piu&amp;rsquo; facile entrare&amp;rdquo;,&amp;nbsp;e tantomeno ho portato un esempio. Eppure, sono ormai MIGLIAIA le persone che si sono descritte, piu&amp;rsquo; o meno, allo stesso modo.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;LA sfiga e&amp;rsquo; che poi si scopre che non e&amp;rsquo; cosi&amp;rsquo;. Tempo fa ci furono dei post tipo &amp;ldquo;cosa mi piace leggere&amp;rdquo; o &amp;ldquo;cosa mi piace fare&amp;rdquo;, e il risultato e&amp;rsquo; che non solo&amp;nbsp;esistono hobbies che non pensavo esistessero, ma che in ultima analisi SIETE persone mediamente interessanti.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;Quello che vedo e&amp;rsquo; una strana coincidenza tra due fatti completamente opposti:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;ul style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;li style=&#34;line-height: 17px; text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;Il primo e&amp;rsquo; che tutti voi, nel descrivervi, apparite assolutamente annoiati, pessimisti, privi di autostima, persi nel vuoto.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&#34;line-height: 17px; text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;Il secondo e&amp;rsquo; che poi, nella realta&amp;rsquo;, come emerge &amp;nbsp;nel parlare e scambiarsi interessi, fate cose, vedete gente, e tutto quanto.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Siete molto migliori delle persone che credete di essere. E quelli che credete essere migliori di voi sono, onestamente - e me ne sono reso conto nelle vicende che conoscete - delle nauseanti distese di piccole miserie umane, &lt;i&gt;vite indegne di essere vissute&lt;/i&gt;.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;Questo fenomeno si chiama &amp;ldquo;Disforia&amp;rdquo;. Come la disforia di genere si definisce nella percezione di se&amp;rsquo; risultante in un sesso opposto a quello biologico,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;la vostra stravagante disforia e&amp;rsquo; di percepire voi stessi come persone molto meno interessanti di quanto non siate poi, se coinvolti in una discussione.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;Cosi&amp;rsquo; sono andato indietro a rileggere le discussioni. E ho notato un fenomeno ancora piu&amp;rsquo; interessante, per chi ha interesse nell&amp;rsquo;umanita&amp;rsquo;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;Tutti i thread ove si parlava, che so, di che cosa vi piace fare o che cosa vi piace leggere mostravano quello che definirei un &amp;ldquo;profondo senso di liberazione&amp;rdquo;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;La sensazione che ho e&amp;rsquo; che dire &amp;ldquo;a me piace leggere saggistica sui canguri&amp;rdquo; abbia prodotto circa la stessa liberazione che si prova facendo una specie di&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;coming-out, ovvero: nella vita comune devo NASCONDERE che mi piace studiare la storia dei canguri , mentre finalmente qui posso dirlo. Aha.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;Aha una cippa. Voglio dire, qui non si tratta di un effetto pigmalione al contrario. Qui si tratta di una sistematica oppressione, che si propone di costringere&amp;nbsp;ognuno a:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;ul style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;li style=&#34;line-height: 17px; text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;Nascondere di avere qualsiasi interesse, per evitare di venire assalito da chi, essendo mediocre, teme di essere sorpassato.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&#34;line-height: 17px; text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;Costringere chi ha interessi a considerarsi piu&amp;rsquo; debole , meno interessante, meno creativo, PIU&amp;rsquo; SOLO: vivere la propria passione in CLANDESTINITA&amp;rsquo;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&#34;line-height: 17px; text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;Devastare l&amp;rsquo;autostima di chiunque mostri di uscire dalla mediocrita&amp;rsquo;, in modo che non abbia mai il coraggio di mostrarsi, di socializzare con altri, di mostrarsi per cosa e&amp;rsquo;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&#34;line-height: 17px; text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;Ridurre queste persone all&amp;rsquo;INVISIBILITA&amp;rsquo;, lasciando spazio di visibilita&amp;rsquo; SOLO a chi e&amp;rsquo; assolutamente mediocre, ma (attraverso il gruppo) e&amp;rsquo; aggressivo e incombente.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;Se io dicessi a tutte queste persone come fare, in che modo uscire da tutto questo, diventerei il santone di una setta. Cosa che non ho intenzione di essere o diventare.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;D&amp;rsquo;altro canto, la chiusura del blog mi ha spinto a chiedermi che forza mi spingesse a scrivere. E sia, l&amp;rsquo;ho capito.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;L&amp;rsquo;irrequietezza.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;Poi pero&amp;rsquo; devo chiedermi a chi scrivo, per chi scrivo, che cosa scrivo.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;Probabilmente mi illudevo nel dire che il blog NON HA scopi. Era falso. Vedere migliaia di persone letteralmente distrutte nell&amp;rsquo;autostima , soltanto perche&amp;rsquo; si e&amp;rsquo; voluta minare&amp;nbsp;la loro sicurezza ed autonomia (e credetemi, emigrare vi insegna quanto conti l&amp;rsquo;autostima!) allo scopo di &amp;ldquo;tenerli cagati&amp;rdquo; non mi piace per niente.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;Questa mailing list e&amp;rsquo; servita negli scorsi mesi come luogo di &amp;ldquo;coming out&amp;rdquo;, ma questo non ha alcun senso: non ho la fiducia che ha Pahlaniuk nei gruppi&amp;nbsp;di supporto, e penso che troppo facilmente si trasformano in delle vere e proprie sette. E che se un processo del genere avviene solo nel chiuso, non serve a niente:&amp;nbsp;il fight club e&amp;rsquo; una merda perche&amp;rsquo; si nasconde, cosa che nessun guerriero fa.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;Nell&amp;rsquo;investigare su quel che provo nella chiusura del blog, sto un pochino ridisegnando il mondo attorno a me, nel senso di capire come mai voglio scrivere,&amp;nbsp;perche&amp;rsquo; scrivo, a chi scrivo, cosa scrivo. Questo e&amp;rsquo; un periodo di investigazione riguardo a me stesso, che pero&amp;rsquo; in qualche modo coinvolge anche voi.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;Credo che a breve Kein Pfusch riaprira&amp;rsquo;. Forse ha gia&amp;rsquo; riaperto, in questa mia nuova consapevolezza.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;Ma sara&amp;rsquo; diverso da prima, perche&amp;rsquo; chiudere mi ha costretto a chiedermi perche&amp;rsquo; scrivo. Che forza mi spinge, a chi scrivo, perche&amp;rsquo; .&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;Nel senso che ora so perche&amp;rsquo;, so a chi, so per chi, so CONTRO chi, e so cosa scrivere.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;Credo sia ora di creare uno specchio. Uno specchio impossibile.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;Uno specchio che vi mostri voi stessi, che vi faccia capire che NON siete delle merde, che le merde sono quelle che vi hanno tolto l&amp;rsquo;autostima solo perche&amp;rsquo; non vi bastava l&amp;rsquo;anestetico che fa dormire loro.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;Qualcosa che , in definitiva, spezzi questo assurdo pseudo-pudore per il quale i migliori sono spinti a disprezzare se&amp;rsquo; stessi, e ad ammirare i peggiori.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;Si tratta di un meme da seminare, in fondo.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;I salici si piegano al vento, a volte sino al suolo. Sopportano l&amp;rsquo;umiliazione per dedizione ad un terribile scopo, piu&amp;rsquo; importante di ogni altra cosa: produrre altri salici.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;text-align: justify;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;E quando i salici saranno in numero sufficiente, fermeranno il vento, senza alcuno sforzo particolare.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;Il blog continuera&amp;rsquo; a parlare delle cose che mi va di dire. Rimane un percorso personale. Ma adesso scrivero&amp;rsquo; le stesse cose in un&amp;rsquo;ottica molto, molto, molto diversa da prima.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;Come al solito, ringrazio tutti quelli che mi hanno fatto del male, per avermi reso piu&amp;rsquo; forte.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-family: inherit;&#34;&gt;Va da se&amp;rsquo; che verrete ripagati.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;background-color: white; color: #222222;&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
